[metadata]
Name:Seismic Sense Dig From Own Library
Goal:Win
Difficulty:Easy
Description:Regression for mtg-415 — Dig (target_self=true) must move the top creature/land of the digger's library to hand. Library has Ostrich-Horse on top, then 5 Forests; with 1 Forest in play X=1 so Seismic Sense looks at 1 card and keeps it. Pre-fix the network shadow client failed the ChangeValid filter and put the card on the bottom instead; this puzzle pins the local single-player behaviour so the routing through choose_from_library_with_hook stays correct.

